          "name": "What represents the 'basics' in a Perry Ellis portfolio?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "The basics or foundational pieces in this portfolio analogy represent broad-market index funds, blue-chip dividend stocks, and high-quality bonds that provide stability and steady, long-term growth regardless of market 'seasons'."
